<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
    <title>Results</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Survey results</h1>

    <p>Total number of surveys: <%= rowCount %></p>
    <p>Average age: <%= aveAge %></p>
    <p>Oldest person who participated in survey: <%= old %></p>
    <p>Youngest person who participated in survey: <%= young %></p>
    <br />
    <p>Percentage of people who like Pizza: <%= pizza %></p>
    <p>Percentage of people who like Pasta: <%= pasta %></p>
    <p>Percentage of people who like Pap and Wors: <%= papAndWors %></p>
    <br />
    <p>People like to eat out: <%= aveEatOut %></p>
    <p>People like to watch movies: <%= aveWatchMovies %></p>
    <p>People like to watch TV: <%= aveWatchTv %></p>
    <p>People like to listen to the radio: <%= aveListenRadio %></p>
    <br />
    <button onclick="redirectToHome()">OK</button>

    <script>
        function redirectToHome() {
        window.location.href = "http://localhost:3000/";
      }
    </script>
</body>
</html>